WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 20=

01:38.490 --> 01:39.330
Yunke.

01:41.620 --> 01:42.460
Dear?

01:43.740 --> 01:44.690
You came so late.

01:45.180 --> 01:46.280
Is there some urgent matter?

01:58.540 --> 02:00.130
Your affairs are urgent matters.

02:00.740 --> 02:01.930
Ever since you returned,

02:02.180 --> 02:03.849
you have either been busy
with sect duties

02:03.860 --> 02:05.393
or in seclusion regulating your breath.

02:06.020 --> 02:07.320
On this trip,

02:07.620 --> 02:08.610
were you injured?

02:08.610 --> 02:09.450
Dear,

02:10.010 --> 02:10.850
no need to worry.

02:11.170 --> 02:12.010
I have merely

02:12.400 --> 02:13.460
been traveling for days

02:13.899 --> 02:14.866
and am somewhat fatigued.

02:17.980 --> 02:18.820
That is good.

02:19.500 --> 02:21.660
Nanny Mao and I followed
an ancient recipe

02:21.660 --> 02:22.730
to brew a nourishing soup.

02:23.170 --> 02:24.380
It replenishes qi

02:24.890 --> 02:26.100
and helps restore inner power.

02:26.780 --> 02:29.010
I've asked Lingbo
to deliver some to Yuzhi.

02:29.540 --> 02:30.533
Have some while it's hot.

02:31.570 --> 02:33.820
Yuzhi has medicine from Xiuming.

02:34.170 --> 02:36.220
I'm afraid he can't take other remedies.

02:37.060 --> 02:38.130
It doesn't matter.

02:38.130 --> 02:39.780
It's still Lingbo's heartfelt intention.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.410
You don't know.

02:41.690 --> 02:43.570
During the days you
and Yuzhi were away,

02:43.890 --> 02:45.570
Lingbo was deeply worried.

02:46.220 --> 02:48.410
She almost went to look for you,

02:48.410 --> 02:49.820
yet feared she would be of no help,

02:49.831 --> 02:51.170
so she could only wait in anguish.

02:52.890 --> 02:53.730
Thank you, dear.

02:55.130 --> 02:56.780
Lingbo has indeed grown up.

02:57.170 --> 02:58.010
She's sensible now.

02:58.340 --> 02:59.380
She's sensible,

02:59.980 --> 03:01.620
but her thoughts
have also grown heavier.

03:02.220 --> 03:03.060
Yunke,

03:03.610 --> 03:04.540
I know you are busy,

03:05.430 --> 03:07.210
but Lingbo and Yuzhi's marriage

03:07.660 --> 03:09.410
must be prepared sooner or later.

03:10.660 --> 03:11.890
Such a serious matter

03:12.610 --> 03:14.100
should be considered carefully.

03:14.570 --> 03:15.980
What is there to consider?

03:16.500 --> 03:17.940
What a woman seeks in life

03:17.940 --> 03:19.730
is but a thoughtful husband.

03:19.730 --> 03:21.290
Yuzhi is both virtuous and talented,

03:21.290 --> 03:22.780
and he and Lingbo grew up together.

03:23.130 --> 03:25.100
Yuzhi will surely treat Lingbo well.

03:26.380 --> 03:28.380
That requires
both of them to be willing.

03:29.540 --> 03:31.340
Lingbo has admired Yuzhi
since childhood.

03:31.660 --> 03:32.706
Why would she be unwilling?

03:36.940 --> 03:37.780
Dear,

03:38.570 --> 03:39.500
Yuzhi has always had

03:39.500 --> 03:41.010
his own mind.

03:41.570 --> 03:43.290
If I force him,

03:43.890 --> 03:45.440
it may backfire.

03:45.940 --> 03:47.270
Is it that he has his own mind,

03:47.940 --> 03:48.820
or

03:49.340 --> 03:51.020
has his heart belonged to another?

03:55.340 --> 03:56.180
Dear,

03:56.890 --> 03:57.970
what do you mean by that?

04:03.890 --> 04:04.820
I mean,

04:05.780 --> 04:08.010
is he like you were back then?

04:09.540 --> 04:11.220
After spending time with a Cai,

04:11.890 --> 04:13.130
did affection grow with time,

04:13.730 --> 04:15.610
so he forgot his duty

04:15.980 --> 04:17.660
and loved someone else?

04:18.930 --> 04:19.980
I won't drink it.

04:21.050 --> 04:22.330
- Get out.
- Qi Yunke.

04:22.980 --> 04:24.730
Cai Pingshu is dead, not you.

04:25.140 --> 04:26.980
You refuse treatment and medicine,

04:26.980 --> 04:28.026
and you won't speak to me.

04:28.410 --> 04:29.250
What do you mean?

04:29.730 --> 04:30.570
Get out.

04:31.810 --> 04:32.660
Get out of here.

04:33.250 --> 04:34.100
What did you say?

04:34.980 --> 04:35.980
You told me to get out?

04:36.700 --> 04:38.170
Qi Yunke, have you gone mad?

04:38.660 --> 04:40.050
This is Qingque Sect,

04:40.050 --> 04:40.930
not Luoying Valley.

04:41.170 --> 04:42.490
I'm your wife,

04:42.490 --> 04:43.900
the Lord's wife.

04:45.290 --> 04:46.340
The Lord's wife?

04:46.900 --> 04:48.780
It was you who caused Pingshu's death.

04:48.780 --> 04:49.630
It was you!

04:49.630 --> 04:51.490
What does her death have to do with me?

04:59.370 --> 05:01.980
You are my husband.

05:03.930 --> 05:06.020
We've been married for years.

05:07.290 --> 05:10.050
I've done everything I should.

05:10.900 --> 05:13.170
Yet you exhaust yourself
for another woman.

05:13.170 --> 05:16.140
Every time you return,
your cultivation is drained.

05:16.140 --> 05:18.140
I'm merciful enough
not to reason with her.

05:18.780 --> 05:20.140
It's good that she is dead.

05:20.580 --> 05:22.100
You can finally give up.

05:23.250 --> 05:24.980
You no longer need to save her.

05:24.980 --> 05:25.820
I'm useless.

05:27.540 --> 05:28.380
I couldn't save her.

05:29.700 --> 05:31.020
I couldn't!

05:34.140 --> 05:35.100
You are useless.

05:36.370 --> 05:38.610
The Lord of Qingque Sect

05:39.220 --> 05:41.250
is shedding tears
for an unrelated woman.

05:42.020 --> 05:43.540
What righteous light?

05:44.050 --> 05:45.980
What Ms. Cai?

05:46.370 --> 05:48.340
Everyone says Cai Pingshu

05:48.340 --> 05:49.706
fought Nie Hengcheng for the world

05:50.370 --> 05:53.850
until both were gravely wounded.

05:53.850 --> 05:55.700
But I only resent that wretch

05:55.700 --> 05:57.192
for taking so many years to die.

05:57.203 --> 05:58.340
She should've died long ago.

05:58.340 --> 05:59.180
Stop talking.

06:00.220 --> 06:01.060
What?

06:01.540 --> 06:02.980
Instead of wailing here,

06:03.410 --> 06:04.912
you might as well go to Luoying Valley

06:04.923 --> 06:05.900
and be buried with her.

06:08.220 --> 06:09.060
Oh, yes.

06:10.490 --> 06:11.700
I just remembered.

06:12.700 --> 06:14.410
She had Zhou Zhizhen.

06:14.410 --> 06:16.660
She had so many brothers.

06:16.660 --> 06:18.020
It would not even be your turn.

06:18.290 --> 06:19.130
Enough.

06:33.980 --> 06:34.820
Get up.

06:40.350 --> 06:42.220
This ungrateful, filthy place

06:43.220 --> 06:44.180
is not worth staying in.

06:44.340 --> 06:45.180
Let's go.

06:48.700 --> 06:49.660
Wait.

06:50.730 --> 06:51.730
Chang,

06:53.410 --> 06:54.370
I can't leave.

06:56.250 --> 06:57.900
However unbearable this place is,

06:59.810 --> 07:01.220
I must endure it.

07:09.370 --> 07:11.140
Because I'm the Lord.

07:20.660 --> 07:21.540
Lord Qi,

07:25.410 --> 07:26.250
take care.

07:55.780 --> 07:56.620
Dear,

07:58.220 --> 07:59.290
just now,

07:59.850 --> 08:01.540
I had disordered meridians

08:02.730 --> 08:04.850
and nearly fell into deviation.

08:07.250 --> 08:08.540
Please don't blame me.

08:15.370 --> 08:17.610
It seems my obsession is too deep.

08:18.250 --> 08:20.290
Yuzhi has his own ideas.

08:21.100 --> 08:22.660
Once he decides,

08:23.220 --> 08:24.779
he won't easily change.

08:24.790 --> 08:25.777
But do you still remember

08:25.788 --> 08:27.490
what you promised my father
and my sister?

08:27.490 --> 08:28.610
I haven't forgotten.

08:28.610 --> 08:30.140
I promised your father

08:31.100 --> 08:32.370
to take good care of you

08:32.980 --> 08:34.530
and never let you suffer.

08:34.530 --> 08:35.700
I haven't broken that promise.

08:36.010 --> 08:37.770
I also promised your sister

08:37.770 --> 08:39.060
to raise Yuzhi well.

08:39.060 --> 08:40.530
I haven't broken that either.

08:40.530 --> 08:41.850
What about Lingbo?

08:41.850 --> 08:43.282
She's your daughter.

08:43.293 --> 08:45.329
Even if she and Yuzhi
are fated to miss each other,

08:45.340 --> 08:47.220
you should choose
another good husband for her.

08:47.220 --> 08:48.820
Precisely because she is my daughter,

08:48.820 --> 08:50.610
I hope she can

08:50.610 --> 08:52.490
be joyful every day,

08:52.490 --> 08:53.850
rather than forcing herself

08:53.850 --> 08:54.940
into a mistaken marriage.

09:30.890 --> 09:33.010
(Why can't I advance the Ziwei Method?)

09:33.980 --> 09:34.980
(Did I miss something?)

09:35.340 --> 09:36.340
(The Ziwei Method.)

09:37.250 --> 09:38.490
(Take the resilience of gold.)

09:38.770 --> 09:39.940
(Take the firmness of jade.)

09:40.370 --> 09:41.490
(Refine bones with gold.)

09:41.770 --> 09:43.100
(Temper the heart with jade.)

09:43.610 --> 09:44.980
This Jade Sunflower

09:44.980 --> 09:46.850
is merely a healing item

09:46.850 --> 09:48.980
to calm the mind and warm the meridians.

09:48.980 --> 09:50.890
Why would Nie Hengcheng value it so much

09:51.770 --> 09:54.130
that he'd injure his trusted disciple?

09:54.130 --> 09:56.890
Lu Chengnan was even the next chief.

09:57.420 --> 09:59.180
Why offend Nie Hengcheng

09:59.580 --> 10:01.010
over a mere object?

10:02.060 --> 10:03.010
The Jade Sunflower.

10:09.730 --> 10:10.820
Greetings, Young Master.

10:14.023 --> 10:15.603
I called you here for nothing important.

10:16.300 --> 10:17.246
I only wish to ask

10:17.257 --> 10:18.646
what you plan to do in the future.

10:18.820 --> 10:20.060
You're merciful.

10:21.450 --> 10:23.130
Si'en and I are deeply grateful.

10:23.730 --> 10:24.850
After we leave this time,

10:24.850 --> 10:26.653
we'll find a secluded village

10:26.664 --> 10:28.166
and spend the rest of our lives there,

10:28.850 --> 10:31.180
never again entangled with Li Sect.

10:33.580 --> 10:34.420
Rise.

10:36.820 --> 10:38.730
We don't have freedom in Jianghu.

10:39.086 --> 10:40.512
Love and hatred are hard to sever.

10:40.650 --> 10:42.180
My father also once wished

10:43.220 --> 10:45.010
to live alone
and pass his days in peace.

10:45.890 --> 10:47.130
I still remember back then,

10:47.130 --> 10:48.530
my father was on good terms

10:48.530 --> 10:50.610
with you and Lu Chengnan.

10:50.610 --> 10:51.940
I wonder whether Elder Lu

10:53.650 --> 10:54.770
is still alive.

10:55.650 --> 10:56.490
Yes.

10:57.180 --> 10:59.490
There has been no news of Lu
for a long time.

10:59.980 --> 11:01.300
Among the many elders of Li Sect,

11:02.160 --> 11:04.130
Elder Lu was the most loyal and brave.

11:04.730 --> 11:05.890
Yet his whole life

11:06.340 --> 11:07.613
was trapped by those two words.

11:08.010 --> 11:09.220
After he left,

11:09.770 --> 11:11.330
my foster father's temperament changed.

11:11.650 --> 11:13.100
Everyone was overwhelmed.

11:13.490 --> 11:15.370
There were no more banquets in the sect,

11:15.370 --> 11:18.250
no more music from Mr. Mu Zhengming,

11:19.300 --> 11:20.850
nor the fragrance of the Osmanthus Wine

11:20.850 --> 11:23.340
Lu loved most.

11:26.940 --> 11:27.940
Osmanthus Wine?

11:30.250 --> 11:31.250
It's late.

11:32.610 --> 11:33.730
Go back and rest early.

11:34.130 --> 11:34.980
Take care.

11:34.980 --> 11:36.010
Take care, Young Master.

11:54.250 --> 11:55.340
Osmanthus Wine.

11:58.300 --> 12:00.130
The company of osmanthus flowers now

12:00.890 --> 12:02.580
will never match the days of youth.

12:04.500 --> 12:05.740
(Osmanthus Wine)
Cheers.

12:09.100 --> 12:11.490
(Could the old friend
Mr. Chang was honoring)

12:11.490 --> 12:12.700
(be Lu Chengnan?)

12:15.060 --> 12:15.900
Young Master.

12:17.890 --> 12:18.730
Young Master.

12:19.420 --> 12:20.260
What is it?

12:20.310 --> 12:21.180
Young Master,

12:21.190 --> 12:22.580
you can't let Miss Cai get married.

12:23.100 --> 12:24.010
Married?

12:24.010 --> 12:25.580
It's said Qi Yunke

12:25.580 --> 12:26.940
is preparing a wedding

12:26.940 --> 12:28.060
for Miss Cai and Zhou.

12:28.060 --> 12:29.180
I asked Shangguan.

12:29.180 --> 12:30.250
The Thousandfold Cliff

12:30.250 --> 12:31.700
is not iron.

12:31.700 --> 12:32.590
Why don't we

12:32.590 --> 12:33.940
storm Qingque Sect directly

12:33.940 --> 12:35.220
and snatch Miss Cai back?

12:36.610 --> 12:38.820
She'll marry Zhou Yuqi?

12:39.100 --> 12:40.580
I don't even know

12:41.010 --> 12:42.250
where this Zhou Yuqi came from.

12:42.770 --> 12:44.530
I can accept Mr. Song.

12:44.530 --> 12:45.370
But Zhou...

12:57.980 --> 12:59.850
Why cry while embroidering?

13:03.700 --> 13:05.340
You're about to marry.

13:06.010 --> 13:07.610
I'm happy, so I want

13:07.610 --> 13:09.300
to embroider two mandarin ducks for you.

13:10.490 --> 13:11.820
But when I think

13:12.036 --> 13:13.689
that after Miss Cai becomes
the mistress,

13:15.010 --> 13:16.060
we'll never again have

13:16.060 --> 13:17.300
such days as these,

13:17.940 --> 13:19.010
I can't bear it.

13:21.490 --> 13:22.330
Xinrou.

13:27.650 --> 13:28.980
All right, don't cry.

13:29.300 --> 13:30.300
Zhao is gentle.

13:30.300 --> 13:31.610
She won't cast you aside.

13:32.530 --> 13:34.580
Just stay in the manor at ease.

13:35.100 --> 13:35.940
All right?

13:36.730 --> 13:37.570
Don't cry.

14:03.250 --> 14:04.090
Why did Aunt

14:04.850 --> 14:06.940
give up Uncle Zhou back then?

14:09.610 --> 14:11.340
Was it because
of the skin-painted demon?

14:15.890 --> 14:16.730
Zhao,

14:17.010 --> 14:18.180
in all matters, do your best

14:18.180 --> 14:19.340
and follow your heart.

14:20.370 --> 14:21.940
My mother once said

14:21.940 --> 14:23.580
that choices are the hardest to make.

14:23.580 --> 14:25.420
Listen carefully
to the voice in your heart,

14:26.010 --> 14:27.530
and you will know what to do.

14:31.530 --> 14:32.490
Are you hurt?

14:38.610 --> 14:40.250
I don't think I want to marry Yuqi.

14:56.060 --> 14:58.770
The Sunflower might've been taken
to the Chang clan by Lu Chengnan.

14:58.770 --> 15:00.890
The massacre may be related to him.

15:02.420 --> 15:04.113
(The Jade Sunflower
is at the Chang clan?)

15:16.820 --> 15:18.730
Red beans on an exquisite dice.

15:20.580 --> 15:23.420
Do you know I'm missing you?

15:25.220 --> 15:26.306
I don't care who you miss.

15:34.820 --> 15:35.660
Yuzhi.

15:37.370 --> 15:38.210
Zhao.

15:41.490 --> 15:43.490
Lu Chengnan was
Nie Hengcheng's trusted disciple.

15:43.490 --> 15:45.530
So, Mu Qingyan likely spoke the truth.

15:45.850 --> 15:46.690
Zhao,

15:47.180 --> 15:48.213
do you wish to verify it?

15:48.340 --> 15:50.100
Don't you also need the Jade Sunflower?

15:51.610 --> 15:52.890
But the mechanisms of Chang Fort

15:52.890 --> 15:54.300
were set by my aunt.

15:54.300 --> 15:55.833
Lu Chengnan was a demonic disciple.

15:55.844 --> 15:56.877
How could he have entered?

15:58.250 --> 15:59.670
Thinking back to the investigation,

15:59.850 --> 16:00.820
I think it was rushed.

16:01.490 --> 16:02.530
Yuzhi, do you think

16:03.010 --> 16:04.172
there was anything suspicious

16:04.183 --> 16:05.650
we overlooked?

16:05.650 --> 16:07.530
For example, a hidden passage
or secret chamber

16:07.530 --> 16:08.370
we never discovered?

16:08.850 --> 16:09.690
Zhao.

16:11.730 --> 16:12.570
Master.

16:12.820 --> 16:13.660
What are you

16:14.180 --> 16:15.700
discussing so early in the morning?

16:16.130 --> 16:17.790
Yuzhi and I were talking

16:17.801 --> 16:19.220
about the mechanisms of Chang Fort.

16:19.220 --> 16:20.060
Master,

16:20.340 --> 16:22.650
Mr. Chang's death anniversary is near.

16:22.650 --> 16:25.340
I witnessed the tragic scene.

16:25.340 --> 16:27.010
Even now, my heart still aches.

16:27.420 --> 16:28.980
So, I wish to go with Zhao

16:28.980 --> 16:30.100
to pay our respects.

16:31.370 --> 16:32.340
As it should be.

16:33.500 --> 16:35.420
If I were not entangled in sect affairs,

16:35.650 --> 16:36.650
I would go with you.

16:37.330 --> 16:38.250
It's fine, Master.

16:38.980 --> 16:40.700
Yuzhi and I

16:40.700 --> 16:42.730
can offer incense on your behalf.

16:45.610 --> 16:46.450
Very well.

16:54.180 --> 16:56.010
Master, no need to see us off.

16:56.010 --> 16:57.250
It's only a few steps.

16:57.250 --> 16:58.250
It's no trouble.

16:58.250 --> 16:59.890
The scenery is best in this season.

17:00.300 --> 17:01.730
You may stroll around as well.

17:03.700 --> 17:04.540
Yuzhi,

17:05.770 --> 17:07.620
in this bundle, there are banknotes

17:08.050 --> 17:10.980
and some hairpins and bracelets
that girls favor.

17:11.730 --> 17:13.250
Find a time to give them to Zhao.

17:14.250 --> 17:15.140
Father,

17:15.380 --> 17:16.673
we're going to pay our respects.

17:17.380 --> 17:18.220
I know.

17:18.700 --> 17:19.980
Take care of yourself, Master.

17:20.660 --> 17:22.660
Don't let me worry while away.

17:22.660 --> 17:23.530
You too.

17:24.220 --> 17:25.250
When outside,

17:25.250 --> 17:26.490
be cautious in all matters.

17:28.010 --> 17:29.380
Mr. Chang

17:29.380 --> 17:30.810
was righteous and loyal.

17:30.810 --> 17:32.570
You must pay your respects properly.

17:32.860 --> 17:33.700
Zhao,

17:33.900 --> 17:35.220
it's a long journey.

17:35.393 --> 17:36.689
If you need anything on the road,

17:36.700 --> 17:37.730
have this lad run errands.

17:38.180 --> 17:39.730
Don't treat him as an outsider.

17:39.730 --> 17:41.180
Don't worry, Uncle Song.

17:41.180 --> 17:42.620
We'll return in ten days.

17:42.620 --> 17:43.900
I'll take good care of Zhao.

17:44.420 --> 17:46.050
Good. You finally understand.

17:46.050 --> 17:47.290
All right, enough chatter.

17:47.290 --> 17:48.620
Let them set off.

17:48.620 --> 17:49.460
Go on.

17:49.660 --> 17:50.770
Yes, Master.

17:51.140 --> 17:51.980
Go.

17:52.810 --> 17:53.650
Wait.

17:55.330 --> 17:56.170
Wait a moment.

17:57.693 --> 17:59.180
- Why are you all here?
- We made it.

17:59.180 --> 18:00.490
Why carry bundles to see them off?

18:01.010 --> 18:01.850
Uncle.

18:02.090 --> 18:02.940
Father,

18:02.940 --> 18:05.290
don't you always say
I should travel more in Jianghu

18:05.290 --> 18:06.220
to broaden my horizons?

18:06.220 --> 18:08.290
Since Cai Zhao is going to pay respects,

18:08.290 --> 18:09.490
I wish to go as well

18:09.490 --> 18:10.330
and gain experience.

18:10.700 --> 18:11.940
Lingbo lacks experience.

18:11.940 --> 18:13.010
I'll accompany her.

18:13.010 --> 18:14.250
I've long admired

18:14.250 --> 18:15.380
the Chang's Willow Sword.

18:15.380 --> 18:17.420
I wish to pay my respects
at Mr. Chang's grave.

18:18.180 --> 18:19.412
- You...
- Master,

18:19.423 --> 18:20.860
if my senior brothers go without me,

18:20.860 --> 18:22.550
they may not even
settle accounts clearly.

18:22.561 --> 18:24.530
Let me join to honor Mr. Chang.

18:26.230 --> 18:28.690
♪I roam the rivers and hills♪

18:28.690 --> 18:30.000
♪In the martial world♪

18:30.050 --> 18:31.250
It must be a hard journey.

18:31.700 --> 18:32.860
Let me go on your behalf

18:32.860 --> 18:34.860
and pay respects,

18:35.420 --> 18:36.330
Yuqi, Xinrou.

18:36.330 --> 18:37.190
Zhao,

18:37.200 --> 18:39.330
I'm escorting my cousin back.
It's on the way.

18:39.330 --> 18:40.170
It's no trouble.

18:42.140 --> 18:43.380
Father,

18:43.380 --> 18:44.860
please let us go.

18:44.860 --> 18:46.180
- Please.
- Please.

18:46.180 --> 18:47.050
Yes, Master.

18:47.050 --> 18:48.180
Very well.

18:48.180 --> 18:50.250
Travel together
and don't waste your youth.

18:50.250 --> 18:51.090
Go on.

18:51.660 --> 18:52.620
All right then.

18:54.503 --> 18:55.900
- Thanks, Father.
- Thanks, Master.

18:55.900 --> 18:56.740
Let's go.

18:56.980 --> 18:58.180
- Thanks, Master.
- Go.

18:58.180 --> 19:03.170
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

19:07.810 --> 19:08.730
Look.

19:08.730 --> 19:10.050
So many third wheels.

19:11.140 --> 19:12.090
I think so.

19:12.530 --> 19:14.090
How troublesome.

19:14.090 --> 19:16.090
Then why did you not stop them?

19:16.090 --> 19:17.530
You did not stop them either.

19:17.530 --> 19:18.370
You...

19:24.140 --> 19:25.050
Zhao,

19:25.050 --> 19:26.250
Xinrou has caught a chill.

19:26.389 --> 19:27.942
I'll take her to see a physician first.

19:28.250 --> 19:29.620
We'll join you later.

19:30.010 --> 19:31.530
Yuqi, farewell.

19:31.530 --> 19:32.980
Zhao, farewell.

19:56.290 --> 19:57.130
We've arrived.

20:00.180 --> 20:02.620
(Chang Fort)

20:30.330 --> 20:31.170
Chang Ning?

20:31.940 --> 20:32.940
I'm Mu Qingyan

20:33.980 --> 20:35.050
of Li Sect.

20:36.980 --> 20:38.180
The new Chief.

20:38.860 --> 20:40.140
I knew long ago you were a fake.

20:40.810 --> 20:42.330
You schemed to hide in Qingque Sect.

20:42.330 --> 20:43.420
What was your intention?

20:43.940 --> 20:44.860
The Young Master came

20:44.860 --> 20:46.330
to honor an old friend.

20:46.730 --> 20:48.330
We don't wish to stir trouble.

20:49.010 --> 20:50.900
Everyone, no need to be tense.

20:50.900 --> 20:51.466
Nonsense.

20:51.554 --> 20:53.250
The demonic sect massacred
the Chang clan.

20:53.250 --> 20:54.220
What old friend?

20:54.220 --> 20:55.140
Enough talk.

20:55.730 --> 20:56.660
Make your move.

20:57.700 --> 20:58.540
Mr. Mu,

21:13.980 --> 21:15.326
since you don't wish for conflict,

21:15.530 --> 21:16.370
words are useless.

21:17.730 --> 21:18.660
Let's part here.

21:35.090 --> 21:35.930
Let's go.

21:52.620 --> 21:54.780
(Wu'an Inn)

21:54.780 --> 21:58.740
(Wu'an Town)

22:06.900 --> 22:08.180
(Kind and Hospitable)

22:08.180 --> 22:09.570
The anniversary is in three days.

22:10.250 --> 22:11.196
Let's stay here first.

22:11.730 --> 22:13.700
Notify Taichu Temple nearby
to heighten vigilance.

22:14.770 --> 22:15.610
Cai Zhao,

22:16.620 --> 22:18.420
you knew he was the demonic sect chief.

22:18.420 --> 22:19.570
Why let him go?

22:20.180 --> 22:21.250
I can't defeat him.

22:21.250 --> 22:22.490
You can't defeat him?

22:22.490 --> 22:24.010
I think it's not that you can't,

22:24.010 --> 22:25.530
but that you were colluding all along.

22:26.050 --> 22:27.530
Back in Qingque Sect,

22:27.530 --> 22:28.940
you lived together every day.

22:30.900 --> 22:33.420
Zhao must've been deceived by him.

22:33.420 --> 22:34.980
Who deceived whom?

22:34.980 --> 22:37.220
They went in and out together back then.

22:37.220 --> 22:38.810
Cai Zhao defended him time and again.

22:38.810 --> 22:39.650
Lingbo,

22:39.810 --> 22:41.490
if you hadn't bullied Chang then,

22:41.940 --> 22:43.380
why would Zhao have stayed with him?

22:43.860 --> 22:44.810
- You...
- Yuzhi,

22:44.810 --> 22:45.849
Lingbo was insightful

22:45.860 --> 22:47.713
and discovered
that Chang Ning was suspicious.

22:48.250 --> 22:49.980
We shouldn't have let that demon go.

22:49.980 --> 22:50.820
We can't defeat him.

22:53.010 --> 22:54.290
The two men Mu Qingyan brought

22:54.760 --> 22:55.282
had sealed

22:55.293 --> 22:57.140
all our attacking angles
with their positions.

22:57.140 --> 22:57.980
Within 100 moves,

22:58.140 --> 22:59.386
we couldn't have subdued them.

22:59.980 --> 23:01.090
If we truly fought,

23:01.090 --> 23:02.236
we had no chance of victory.

23:04.010 --> 23:04.850
Enough.

23:05.290 --> 23:06.276
We are weary from travel.

23:06.730 --> 23:07.860
Let's rest today.

23:08.380 --> 23:09.250
Boring.

23:09.250 --> 23:10.090
Lingbo.

23:14.710 --> 23:15.570
Lingbo.

23:15.570 --> 23:16.410
Stop calling me.

23:16.860 --> 23:18.250
Weary from travel?

23:18.490 --> 23:19.463
As if he alone is tired.

23:23.980 --> 23:24.820
Zhuo,

23:25.620 --> 23:28.330
I did not see any positioning.

23:28.770 --> 23:30.770
Were they not just standing there?

23:31.290 --> 23:33.490
But their clothing fabric looked fine.

23:33.490 --> 23:34.730
Not found in the market.

23:34.730 --> 23:36.050
The style was novel too.

23:36.050 --> 23:38.180
The demonic sect's tailoring

23:38.620 --> 23:39.460
is truly impressive.

23:40.050 --> 23:41.490
You only noticed their clothes?

23:43.013 --> 23:44.366
Yes, I only noticed their clothes.

23:46.660 --> 23:48.463
I know Mr. Mu is not a bad person.

23:48.474 --> 23:50.239
- But we're...
- We're not on the same side.

23:50.250 --> 23:51.090
Yuzhi,

23:51.570 --> 23:52.420
I know what to do.

24:24.980 --> 24:26.250
You've finally arrived.

24:26.936 --> 24:28.049
I've waited for a long time.

24:31.330 --> 24:33.050
How did you bribe the innkeeper?

24:34.860 --> 24:36.010
I did not bribe him.

24:38.290 --> 24:39.770
I bought the entire inn.

24:40.090 --> 24:41.770
This is the only inn in Wu'an Town.

24:42.420 --> 24:43.620
If you came,

24:44.090 --> 24:45.050
you'd have to stay here.

24:50.010 --> 24:51.730
Don't make futile plans.

24:52.570 --> 24:54.050
After I pay respects to Uncle Chang,

24:54.050 --> 24:55.220
I'll return to Qingque Sect.

24:55.220 --> 24:56.490
And marry Zhou Yuqi?

24:59.530 --> 25:01.290
Such a weak and useless man

25:01.860 --> 25:03.140
can catch your eye?

25:04.140 --> 25:05.560
As I recall, you told me last time

25:05.620 --> 25:08.050
not to meddle in demonic sect affairs.

25:09.010 --> 25:10.002
Then you shouldn't meddle

25:10.013 --> 25:11.683
in the affairs of our Six Sects, either.

25:16.330 --> 25:17.620
You've traveled all day.

25:18.980 --> 25:19.820
Are you hungry?

25:30.480 --> 25:31.766
These just came out of the pot.

25:32.180 --> 25:33.020
Eat while hot.

25:33.620 --> 25:35.290
If left too long,

25:35.290 --> 25:36.290
the skin will turn soggy.

26:09.290 --> 26:10.130
Shangguan,

26:10.306 --> 26:11.972
do you think Miss Cai
and the Young Master

26:12.010 --> 26:12.860
are fighting,

26:13.013 --> 26:14.482
or reuniting after a long separation,

26:14.566 --> 26:15.692
or full of tender affection?

26:16.620 --> 26:17.940
A gentleman does not pry.

26:18.660 --> 26:20.090
Master You, you are too nosy.

26:21.700 --> 26:22.540
If you are not nosy,

26:22.940 --> 26:23.986
why are you standing here?

26:24.250 --> 26:25.770
The Young Master may be in danger.

26:25.963 --> 26:27.103
I'm protecting him in secret.

26:34.620 --> 26:35.460
Tell me.

26:35.896 --> 26:38.015
What was the relationship
between Lu and Uncle Chang?

26:38.620 --> 26:40.220
Why did they bring the Jade Sunflower

26:40.220 --> 26:41.250
to Chang Fort?

26:42.380 --> 26:43.653
After you answer, you may leave.

26:44.256 --> 26:45.900
Others grow soft
after eating one's food.

26:45.900 --> 26:47.050
Yet with you,

26:47.050 --> 26:48.570
you turn hostile before swallowing.

26:49.140 --> 26:51.290
You truly are different.

26:52.220 --> 26:53.060
Forget it then.

26:53.730 --> 26:54.570
I'll tell you.

26:57.940 --> 26:59.490
I deduced it

26:59.490 --> 27:00.530
through Osmanthus Wine.

27:00.933 --> 27:02.940
Before his death,
Mr. Chang brought Osmanthus Wine

27:02.940 --> 27:04.366
to pay respects to an old friend.

27:04.810 --> 27:05.770
And the wine

27:06.380 --> 27:07.730
Lu Chengnan loved most

27:08.290 --> 27:09.380
was Osmanthus Wine.

27:10.140 --> 27:10.980
That is all?

27:12.200 --> 27:14.040
Many in this world

27:14.490 --> 27:15.490
love Osmanthus Wine.

27:15.940 --> 27:16.860
Of course.

27:18.180 --> 27:20.010
Before dying,

27:20.582 --> 27:21.708
Mr. Chang repeatedly told me

27:22.180 --> 27:24.380
the massacre was not aimed at me.

27:25.530 --> 27:26.810
He told me not to feel indebted.

27:27.770 --> 27:29.420
I always thought

27:29.420 --> 27:30.700
he was merely comforting me.

27:31.250 --> 27:32.420
But now I think

27:33.180 --> 27:35.180
he may have spoken the truth.

27:36.090 --> 27:36.930
The Chang clan

27:37.620 --> 27:38.900
was hiding a secret.

27:40.450 --> 27:42.356
Could it be that after Lu
was gravely injured,

27:43.420 --> 27:45.180
he fled to Chang Fort?

27:45.180 --> 27:47.220
The men in black dug through the fort.

27:49.570 --> 27:50.980
I believe they were searching

27:51.940 --> 27:54.330
for the Jade Sunflower
Lu Chengnan had taken.

27:54.810 --> 27:55.700
The Jade Sunflower

27:55.700 --> 27:57.810
is used to dispel cold.

27:57.810 --> 27:59.643
Why would they go
to such lengths to find it,

28:00.330 --> 28:02.050
even exterminating the Chang clan?

28:05.330 --> 28:06.570
The exact reason

28:06.570 --> 28:07.660
is unknown for now.

28:09.290 --> 28:11.330
But since the men in black
did not find it,

28:11.700 --> 28:13.530
it must still be in Chang Fort.

28:14.900 --> 28:16.490
How do you know they did not find it?

28:16.900 --> 28:18.140
If they had,

28:18.860 --> 28:20.380
they wouldn't have gone to such trouble

28:20.380 --> 28:22.490
to abduct Chang Ning at Qingque Sect.

28:24.490 --> 28:25.330
Zhao,

28:26.140 --> 28:27.490
when you returned to Qingque Sect,

28:28.180 --> 28:30.490
did you tell everything truthfully?

28:32.010 --> 28:32.850
Did Lord Qi

28:34.530 --> 28:35.940
say anything about me?

28:37.220 --> 28:39.220
He said you are a skin-painted demon,

28:39.900 --> 28:41.530
wearing human skin convincingly,

28:41.860 --> 28:43.300
but destined to devour hearts.

28:43.620 --> 28:44.660
I'm a skin-painted demon?

28:50.250 --> 28:51.380
If I'm a skin-painted demon,

28:52.530 --> 28:53.490
what are they?

28:55.090 --> 28:56.570
After the Chang massacre,

28:56.900 --> 28:58.020
besides your Luoying Valley,

28:58.570 --> 28:59.980
which of the other five sects

28:59.980 --> 29:02.570
truly wanted to avenge the Changs?

29:03.730 --> 29:04.770
They are all hypocrites.

29:05.810 --> 29:06.860
Even Lord Qi...

29:11.770 --> 29:12.660
Those two

29:13.010 --> 29:13.930
have reconciled again?

29:14.330 --> 29:15.700
The Young Master is mighty.

29:16.050 --> 29:18.140
Subduing Li Sect followers
is nothing to him,

29:18.530 --> 29:19.370
let alone Miss Cai.

29:20.490 --> 29:21.490
I would not even bother

29:21.770 --> 29:22.683
to utter such flattery.

29:25.660 --> 29:27.900
Speaking ill of my elders? Get out.

29:29.050 --> 29:29.980
What is happening?

29:30.530 --> 29:31.620
Are they arguing again?

29:31.950 --> 29:33.170
From my understanding of women,

29:33.770 --> 29:34.730
it should be

29:34.730 --> 29:35.730
the Young Master

29:36.420 --> 29:37.260
being scolded.

29:46.810 --> 29:47.876
Good evening, Young Master.

29:48.900 --> 29:50.810
Such leisure...

29:50.810 --> 29:51.850
Are you admiring the moon?

29:59.290 --> 30:00.290
Yuzhi,

30:00.860 --> 30:02.250
how carefree of you

30:02.530 --> 30:03.380
to admire the moon.

30:03.810 --> 30:04.980
I came to see you, Mr. Mu.

30:11.066 --> 30:12.308
Before I set out, I spread word

30:12.319 --> 30:14.039
that the Jade Sunflower had reappeared.

30:14.250 --> 30:15.770
Nie Zhe and the men in black

30:15.770 --> 30:17.530
have been relentlessly pursuing it.

30:19.140 --> 30:20.770
They should've reached nearby by now.

30:20.770 --> 30:22.490
Nie Zhe caused the Chang massacre.

30:23.290 --> 30:24.530
His crimes are unforgivable.

30:24.530 --> 30:25.723
Naturally, he can't be spared.

30:26.180 --> 30:27.020
However,

30:27.700 --> 30:29.050
capturing Nie Zhe is one matter.

30:29.050 --> 30:31.180
Zhao and I are only here
to pay respects.

30:31.180 --> 30:33.090
Don't put her in a difficult position.

30:33.420 --> 30:34.700
If her reputation is harmed,

30:36.090 --> 30:36.940
it would not be good.

30:37.250 --> 30:38.490
Rumors about you and Zhao

30:38.490 --> 30:39.810
are spreading everywhere.

30:41.140 --> 30:42.940
Does that not affect her reputation?

30:43.290 --> 30:44.530
Song, don't forget.

30:45.050 --> 30:45.890
You are

30:46.900 --> 30:48.180
already betrothed.

30:48.980 --> 30:50.290
I'll handle my betrothal.

30:51.420 --> 30:52.700
No need for you to worry.

30:52.700 --> 30:53.606
How will you handle it?

30:54.010 --> 30:55.770
You shouldn't forget

30:55.770 --> 30:57.860
that Zhao also has a fiancé,

30:57.860 --> 30:59.250
Zhou Yuqi.

31:05.010 --> 31:06.010
I accept

31:09.330 --> 31:10.180
your return gift.

31:16.180 --> 31:17.380
Gaogu Jade can't compare

31:18.420 --> 31:21.010
to the rare stones you gifted.

31:21.330 --> 31:22.323
It's good that you know.

31:29.740 --> 31:30.780
(Kind and Hospitable)

31:30.780 --> 31:32.050
It's hard to imagine

31:32.700 --> 31:34.140
that we'd actually live

31:34.140 --> 31:36.380
under the same roof as the demonic sect

31:36.810 --> 31:38.090
at peace one day.

31:38.860 --> 31:40.090
We are only staying a few days.

31:40.570 --> 31:42.323
If they harbor no ill intent this time,

31:42.334 --> 31:43.773
and both sides refrain from conflict,

31:43.940 --> 31:45.089
that may not be a bad thing.

31:45.250 --> 31:46.270
Have you forgotten, Yuzhi?

31:46.770 --> 31:48.860
They nearly killed Master not long ago.

31:48.860 --> 31:50.330
Such insidious and cunning people

31:50.770 --> 31:52.330
can't be judged by appearances.

31:52.980 --> 31:53.820
Fengchi, don't worry.

31:54.730 --> 31:55.670
I've made arrangements.

31:56.460 --> 31:57.450
After tomorrow,

31:57.700 --> 31:58.770
you'll know.

31:59.380 --> 32:00.220
Good.

32:00.700 --> 32:01.733
We'll wait until tomorrow.

32:04.570 --> 32:05.410
Lingbo,

32:06.420 --> 32:07.940
I've written to inform Master.

32:07.940 --> 32:10.770
In a few days,
he should send instructions.

32:10.770 --> 32:12.090
I wonder what Father would think

32:12.090 --> 32:14.250
if he knew Cai Zhao

32:14.250 --> 32:15.290
and Mu Qingyan

32:16.090 --> 32:17.330
were still entangled.

32:19.090 --> 32:19.930
Lingbo,

32:22.330 --> 32:23.700
I have something to say to you.

32:28.490 --> 32:30.290
Zhou Yuqi and Min Xinrou are here.

32:30.290 --> 32:31.130
I'll go receive them.

32:32.730 --> 32:33.700
Then I'll go practice.

32:45.900 --> 32:46.740
Zhao.

32:50.050 --> 32:50.890
You two talk.

33:00.730 --> 33:01.570
Yuqi,

33:01.810 --> 33:02.650
sit.

33:05.330 --> 33:06.660
Is Min feeling better?

33:07.570 --> 33:08.420
Much better.

33:08.420 --> 33:09.260
She has gone to rest.

33:24.380 --> 33:25.220
Zhao,

33:25.620 --> 33:27.570
did I do something to anger you?

33:30.940 --> 33:33.050
If you mind
that I'm too close to Xinrou,

33:33.050 --> 33:34.730
I'll keep my distance in the future.

33:34.730 --> 33:36.220
But don't blame her because of it.

33:38.570 --> 33:40.420
I no longer mind that matter.

33:41.980 --> 33:42.820
That is good.

33:43.090 --> 33:44.252
Then there will no longer be

33:44.263 --> 33:45.490
those irrelevant people

33:45.490 --> 33:46.420
coming to bother you.

33:50.290 --> 33:51.130
What was that sound?

33:51.730 --> 33:52.940
Most likely a stray cat.

33:53.490 --> 33:54.330
A stray cat?

33:57.330 --> 33:59.420
Quite a mischievous one.

33:59.810 --> 34:00.860
It's asking for a beating.

34:04.660 --> 34:05.500
You filthy cat.

34:05.730 --> 34:06.570
Behave yourself.

34:09.610 --> 34:11.260
Though I don't mind Miss Min,

34:11.260 --> 34:12.650
the marriage between us

34:13.170 --> 34:14.380
can indeed be postponed.

34:16.170 --> 34:17.780
I'm not ready to marry yet.

34:19.900 --> 34:21.650
Do you wish to postpone it,

34:21.650 --> 34:23.420
or do you not wish to marry me at all?

34:24.610 --> 34:25.450
Yuqi,

34:26.170 --> 34:27.420
I need to avenge Uncle Chang

34:28.690 --> 34:30.260
and help Yuzhi clear his poison.

34:30.260 --> 34:31.170
That's too much for me.

34:31.860 --> 34:33.690
I don't wish

34:33.690 --> 34:34.940
to rush into marriage.

34:44.900 --> 34:45.846
Break off the betrothal?

34:47.900 --> 34:49.690
I've asked my father to propose it.

34:50.170 --> 34:51.420
But the timing

34:52.570 --> 34:53.410
is up to you.

34:53.690 --> 34:55.130
What if I don't agree?

34:55.130 --> 34:55.980
I'm willing to wait.

34:55.980 --> 34:57.340
Then wait a lifetime.

35:01.980 --> 35:03.393
You must be tired from the journey.

35:03.900 --> 35:05.090
You should rest.

35:05.940 --> 35:06.780
Please return.

35:25.860 --> 35:27.820
Is this relentless entanglement

35:28.340 --> 35:29.380
meaningful?

35:29.740 --> 35:31.260
You are not me.

35:31.260 --> 35:32.980
How do you know my joy?

35:33.860 --> 35:35.820
As the Chief,

35:35.820 --> 35:37.170
you bear heavy responsibility.

35:37.170 --> 35:38.780
Can't you consider the greater good?

35:43.090 --> 35:44.860
My father was best

35:44.860 --> 35:47.050
at considering the greater good.

35:47.900 --> 35:48.940
And the result?

35:51.690 --> 35:52.740
With me here,

35:54.050 --> 35:55.130
you will not marry Zhou.

36:02.170 --> 36:03.210
Zhao,

36:03.210 --> 36:04.743
I'll never miss what I seek all my life

36:05.300 --> 36:08.300
and endure in silence forever

36:08.300 --> 36:09.610
like my father.

36:13.060 --> 36:18.050
♪You come to my dreams again♪

36:19.380 --> 36:25.410
♪On this cold day, drunk with wine♪

36:27.380 --> 36:34.130
♪Life shifts, a thousand faces pass by♪

36:36.340 --> 36:37.610
Where is the dice I gave you?

36:38.530 --> 36:39.370
Do you still have it?

36:44.170 --> 36:45.183
I threw it away long ago.

36:48.100 --> 36:55.090
♪Across rivers and mountains,
I roam free and wide♪

37:00.010 --> 37:01.380
(As long as I live,)

37:02.690 --> 37:03.530
(I will never)

37:04.860 --> 37:06.650
(let go of you.)

37:15.340 --> 37:16.180
Zhao.

37:20.010 --> 37:21.260
I did not see you at dinner.

37:21.740 --> 37:22.580
No appetite?

37:24.820 --> 37:27.490
You've been so attentive lately.

37:27.501 --> 37:29.821
Nothing like the you who went
to the demonic sect with me.

37:31.860 --> 37:33.570
When we went to the Youming Path,

37:33.570 --> 37:35.130
I shouldn't have focused only on myself

37:35.130 --> 37:36.260
and neglected you.

37:36.260 --> 37:37.460
I'll be mindful in the future.

37:38.260 --> 37:39.100
I'm not important.

37:39.650 --> 37:41.420
Just take good care of Lingbo.

37:43.940 --> 37:45.376
I've spoken frankly with Lingbo.

37:45.387 --> 37:47.147
When we return,
I'll dissolve the betrothal.

37:50.860 --> 37:51.820
Zhao,

37:55.340 --> 37:56.180
I...

37:57.601 --> 38:08.261
=Generation to Generation=

38:27.021 --> 38:31.431
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:31.996 --> 38:36.611
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:36.951 --> 38:41.516
